title: So I finally read the lore and figured out T.F.'s last name
body:
TF.

Twisted Fate.

First name Tobias. That's another T.

The F must be his real last name.

http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/arresteddevelopment/images/a/ab/Arrested-development_(6).jpg/revision/latest?cb=20130521213519

T.F.

Tobias Fünke.
